Package: mx-datetime
Architecture: any
Depends: chrony,
         util-linux-extra,
         xdg-utils | mx-viewer,
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Date and time configuration tool for MX Linux
 MX Date & Time is a graphical utility that allows users to easily
 configure system date, time, and timezone settings. It provides
 a simple interface for synchronizing with time servers using chrony
 and managing date/time preferences without requiring command line
 knowledge.
